<title>
Precautions for Diagnosing Trouble
</title>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Immobilizer control system is controlled by keyless start control module and ECM. Before confirming diagnosing troubles, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70AA500001">Precautions for Diagnosing Trouble</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Before using scan tool, read its “Operator’s (Instructions) Manual” to know how to use it.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Be sure to clear all DTCs after completing troubleshooting.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</servinfo>
